title: STOP SEARCHING! YOU FOUND YOUR DREAM HOME! PLUS Move in w/ $0 Deposit!
posting_body: ['1433 8th Street Northeast, Auburn, WA 98002', 'Neely Station Apartments in Auburn, WAHere at Neely Station, our residents enjoy a long list of amenities that will add an exciting twist to your lifestyle.', "Whether it's lounging by the resort-style pool, hanging out with friends in the evening by our fire pit, getting a quick workout in at the fitness center, or enjoying the billiards table in the clubhouse, you're bound to enjoy yourself.", '\xa0Neely Station is conveniently located on the bus line, and just a few minutes from Green River Community College and Boeing!', 'We also have quick access to WA-167 and Hwy 18.', 'Stop by today for a tour!', 'Apartment Features:', 'New Flooring', 'Pantries', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Storage Space(s)', 'Washer/Dryer', 'Custom Cabinetry', 'Community Features:', 'Fire Pit with Seating Area', 'Translation Service Available', 'BBQ Grills', 'Resident Lounge', 'Billiards', 'Reserved Parking Available', 'Pet Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs Allowed', '2 Pet Limit Per Home', '$250 Pet Fee (Non Refundable)', '$250 Pet Deposit (Refundable)', '$25 Monthly Pet Rent', 'Breed Restrictions Apply', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
